║ M) BPMN → PlantUML Activity Mapping                              ║
╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

  EA BPMN → PlantUML mapping table:

  StartEvent (None)            → start
  StartEvent (Message)         → :✉ReceiveMessage< (AcceptEvent)
  StartEvent (Timer)           → :⏱TimerStart<
  StartEvent (Conditional)     → :❓ConditionalStart<
  StartEvent (Signal)          → :📡SignalStart<
  EndEvent (None)              → stop
  EndEvent (Terminate)         → end
  EndEvent (Error)             → :❌ErrorEnd;  kill
  EndEvent (Message)           → :>SendEndMessage;  stop
  EndEvent (Signal)            → :>📡SignalEnd;  stop
  Task / UserTask              → :Nazwa zadania;
  ServiceTask                  → :⚙Nazwa serwisu;
  SendTask                     → :>Wyślij wiadomość;
  ReceiveTask                  → :<Odbierz wiadomość;
  ManualTask                   → :🖐Zadanie manualne;
  BusinessRuleTask             → :📋Reguła biznesowa;
  ScriptTask                   → :💻Skrypt;
  SubProcess                   → partition "SubProcess" { ... }
  CallActivity                 → :=CallActivity;
  ExclusiveGateway             → if (...) then ... else ... endif
  ParallelGateway              → fork ... fork again ... end fork
  InclusiveGateway             → split ... split again ... end split
  EventBasedGateway            → split z AcceptEvent w gałęziach
  ComplexGateway               → if z wieloma gałęziami + komentarz
  Pool                         → |Pool|
  Lane                         → |Lane|
  SequenceFlow                 → --> lub -> z label
  MessageFlow                  → ..> (dashed)
  DataObject                   → :DaneName/ + note <<dataObject>>
  DataStore                    → :DaneName/ + note <<dataStore>>
  TextAnnotation               → note
  Group                        → partition "GroupName" { ... }
  BoundaryEvent (interrupting)  → detach + note
  BoundaryEvent (non-interrupt) → floating note

