║ MAPOWANIE EA NON-BPMN → BPMN                                     ║
╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

Activity Diagram → BPMN:
  Activity            → process
  Action              → task
  Decision            → exclusiveGateway (diverging)
  MergeNode           → exclusiveGateway (converging)
  ForkNode            → parallelGateway (diverging)
  JoinNode            → parallelGateway (converging)
  InitialNode         → startEvent
  ActivityFinal       → endEvent
  FlowFinal           → endEvent (terminate)
  ControlFlow         → sequenceFlow
  ObjectFlow          → sequenceFlow + dataObject
  Partition/Swimlane  → lane
  SendSignal          → intermediateThrowEvent (signal)
  AcceptEvent         → intermediateCatchEvent
  AcceptTime          → intermediateCatchEvent (timer)
  CallBehavior        → callActivity
  StructuredNode      → subProcess
  ExpansionRegion     → subProcess (loopCharacteristics=multiInstance)
  ExceptionHandler    → boundaryEvent (error) + sequenceFlow
  InterruptibleRegion → subProcess z boundaryEvent
  Pin (Input)         → dataInput
  Pin (Output)        → dataOutput
  ObjectNode          → dataObjectReference
  DataStoreNode       → dataStoreReference

Use Case → BPMN:
  Actor               → participant (pool)
  UseCase             → subProcess lub callActivity
  Include             → sequenceFlow do subProcess
  Extend              → eventSubProcess z conditional start
  System Boundary     → collaboration + pool

State Machine → BPMN:
  State               → task (z state name)
  Transition          → sequenceFlow (z guard jako conditionExpression)
  Decision pseudo.    → exclusiveGateway
  Fork pseudo.        → parallelGateway
  Initial             → startEvent
  Final               → endEvent
  Composite State     → subProcess
  History             → komentarz (brak odpowiednika w BPMN)

Class/Component/Deployment → BPMN:
  TE DIAGRAMY NIE MAJĄ ODPOWIEDNIKA W BPMN.
  → Poinformuj użytkownika: "Diagramy strukturalne (Class, Component, Deployment)
     nie mogą być sensownie zmapowane na BPMN. Pomijam. Użyj PlantUML lub Draw.io."

